The <b>Russian language</b> is one of the more prevalent languages today in the world. Learning this language will significantly help your future employment opportunities. If you don’t already, it will also help you to better understand the Russian culture and prepare for employment there. There are global firms that can help you learn it far easier than most would ever guess. 
<br/><br/>

<h2>Russian Language Resources at the Tip of Your Fingers</h2>
In today's competitive work environment, knowledge of the <b>Russian language</b> gives you an edge. Russian is one of the United Nation's official languages, and is used among governments, international agencies, and non-profit sectors. A wide variety of resources is offered to ensure your ability to communicate effectively in diverse situations, from tourist encounters to business meetings. 
<br/><br/>

<div class="cuadroHome" style="height:210px;">
<img src="/images/home-vocabulary.jpg" title="Vocabulary" alt="Vocabulary">
<h3><a href="/vocabulary/" title="Vocabulary">Vocabulary</a></h3>
Vocabulary words are the building blocks of language. Improve your vocabulary with the word lists provided and you will perform well in business meetings, school settings, and travel encounters.
</div>

<div class="cuadroHome" style="height:210px;">
<img src="/images/home-grammar.jpg" title="Grammar" alt="Grammar">
<h3><a href="/grammar" title="Grammar">Grammar</a></h3>
Improve your grammar with these exercises that will help you to communicate more effectively and eloquently. Russian grammar rules are made clear and easy to understand. 
</div>

<div class="cuadroHome nomargin" style="height:210px;">
<img src="/images/home-pronunciation.jpg" title="Pronunciation" alt="Pronunciation">
<h3><a href="/pronunciation" title="Pronunciation">Pronunciation</a></h3>
Accurate pronunciation is essential. The lessons provided will help you correctly sound out Russian vowels and consonants to ensure you are understood.
</div><br clear="all"><br/>

<h2>Business in Russia is Booming</h2>
<b>International businesses</b> value those with a global perspective and your <b>Russian language skills</b> will show employers that you are the ideal candidate. Russia has the eighth largest economy in the world and is still growing. Russian is also one of the most widely spoken languages throughout many growing countries in Eurasia. Your Russian language skills will give you an advantage during all phases of employment, from <b>searching opportunities</b>, to filling out your application, and improving your skills through further study.
<br/><br/>

<div class="cuadroHome" style="height:230px;">
<img src="/images/home-mba.jpg" title="MBA in Russia" alt="MBA in Russia">
<h3><a href="/business/mba-in-russia" title="MBA in Russia">MBA in Russia</a></h3>
When you get your MBA in Russia you will learn so much valuable information about how international business is pursued. It is free if you work for a Russian company that pays for it as you get work experience in your field.
</div>

<div class="cuadroHome" style="height:230px;">
<img src="/images/home-opportunities.jpg" title="Job Opportunities" alt="Job Opportunities">
<h3><a href="/business/job-opportunities" title="Job Opportunities">Job Opportunities</a></h3>
In today’s global economy, many businesses are seeking applicants with the ability to speak specialized languages. You will be one step ahead of your business counterparts by searching for opportunities in Russia and other post-soviet states where their economies are growing.
</div>

<div class="cuadroHome nomargin" style="height:230px;">
<img src="/images/home-application.jpg" title="Job Application" alt="Job Application">
<h3><a href="/business/job-application" title="Job Application">Job Application</a></h3>
With the language skills provided you will be able to successfully complete job applications for all sectors of employment and market yourself as a competitive candidate for the position.
</div><br clear="all">

<h2>Learning Russian is Easy</h2>
<b>Learning a language</b> can seem complicated, which is why we do the work for you. All the resources, grammar rules, and vocabulary are compiled in an easy-to-navigate format so that you will master Russian in no time. As the economy becomes globalized so do personal relationships. With the <b>online lessons</b> provided, you will be able to communicate with new friends, classmates, and business partners. 
<br><br>

<div class="cuadroHome" style="height:300px">
<img src="/images/home-online.jpg" title="Courses Online" alt="Courses Online">
<h3><a href="/learningrussian/russianonline.asp" title="Courses Online">Courses Online</a></h3>
Learning Russian is simple when you use online courses and other resources that were previously mentioned in this article. When you plan on conducting business in the international community these resources become very valuable. You can learn Russian in an academic setting without having to step foot in a classroom. Take advantage of the teaching tools offered at your own convenience. 
</div>

<div class="cuadroHome" style="height:300px">
<img src="/images/home-abroad.jpg" title="Courses Abroad" alt="Courses Abroad">
<h3><a href="/learningrussian/russianabroad.asp" title="Courses Abroad">Courses Abroad</a></h3>
Some of these Russian schools and courses abroad are available overseas. Eastern Europe offers many of these courses and the experience that you need as well in your future career. This valuable information allows you to not only communicate to your employer and any client. Immersion is one of the most effective ways of mastering a new language and you will also experience the excitement of new customs and culture.

</div>

<div class="cuadroHome nomargin" style="height:300px">
<img src="/images/home-schools.jpg" title="Language Schools" alt="Language Schools">
<h3><a href="/learningrussian/russian-schools" title="Language Schools">Language Schools</a></h3>
You can feel as if you are in Russia from anywhere in the world. Russian schools have the benefits of immersion without having to leave home. All of these resources allow you to learn the Russian language easily and begin to understand the culture so you can further your career in international circles. It is also a wonderful way to gain your MBA for free as you further your work experience in Russian jobs or Russian speaking companies.
</div><br clear="all">


<hr style="clear:both; margin:10px 0; border-top:0; border-left:0; border-right:0; border-bottom:1px solid #ddd">
Russian is the 5th most spoken language in the world. The ability to understand and speak Russian will open doors to a new culture and is a marketable skill in the global economy. The opportunity to travel, study, or work in Russia is an invaluable experience as well as an employment asset.
Once you become more familiar with the Russian language, you will be able to communicate better and understand the culture enough to be capable of finding the best Russian jobs. Once those jobs are won, you will be well on the path to a bright future for your career. You will have experiences that are wonderful and gain exposure to an international market that will provide you with a global view of the world. That will help you as you fill out Russian job applications and get the best positions.
<br><br>
There are online communities that anyone can join to practice Russian and learn more about getting a job there. Many of these sites have lessons, which allow you the chance to learn new words and practice the grammar. The ability to talk to people that have worked there is another benefit of this method. 
<br><br>
Some students find that immersion is one of the most effective means to learn any new language. Learning how to speak it as you gain insight into the culture is an asset that you just can’t pass up if you plan on working in Russia. It is not only one of the best resources that will help you to learn the language, but it also offers a great way to practice the grammar, pronunciation and improve your vocabulary as well.
<br><br>



